						               													<description>This is the card reimplementation of the 2012 board game ZombieZone, for the Board Game of the Month Club.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;ZombieZone is a battle arena where 10 humans and 10 zombies will fight to the death&amp;hellip; on live television. From the safety of our homes, we watch the destruction unfold, placing bets on or against mankind. And some of us will even risk our own lives for a chance at fame and fortune. Will the money hungry-humans, armed with a shotgun and a brain make it out alive? Or will the flesh-hungry Zombies multiply and take them over?&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;ZombieZone is a head to head strategic battle for survival of humans vs. zombies. 2 players each use double-sided disc tokens, cards, and dice to maneuver around a gridded parking lot game board. Humans are armed with a shotgun for ultimate zombie destruction, and zombies spread quickly by taking over the humans (flipping the token over to reveal a zombie on the other side). The last one standing wins.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
